&lt;li&gt;Experience with healthcare SaaS or EHR platforms a plus; prior pre-sales or solutions consulting experience is a bonus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salary range: $80,000-95,000 + variable&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
