&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How We Work&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A typical team at Elation includes 3–5 engineers, an engineering manager, a product manager, a UX designer, and QA working together on a specific product area. Engineers have autonomy over technical implementation decisions while partnering with Product on feature scope and priorities. You’ll own features end-to-end — from architecture and design through deployment and production support.&lt;/p&gt;
