&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute detailed project plans with clearly defined success criteria, milestones, and KPIs that map implementation activities to measurable ROI and clinical outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define, track, and communicate the business value of implementation work, translating operational, financial,&amp;nbsp; and clinical performance metrics into executive-ready insights and progress reports.&lt;/li&gt;
