&lt;li&gt;Champion and embed Elation’s values in every customer and internal interaction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help define and evolve Elation’s next-generation Professional Services model, balancing high-touch strategic guidance with scalable, repeatable delivery mechanisms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
